King West, son of vice chairman Park Management Committee(PMC) in Lagos State Musiliu Akinsanya aka MC Oluomo, has stated that men should have only one wife.   Dancer Korra accuses estranged husband of withdrawing $5,000     Being with Don Jazzy was fun, says ex-wife     Veteran actor Oga Bello celebrates at 70   West, whose father has at least three wives, said getting married to one wife is the best way men can avoid future problems. He wrote on social media: “Guys, to avoid problems for your future, pleas and please marry just one wife.”